伦敦传奇的 MOTH 俱乐部现在面临第二次公寓规划申请的威胁https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-legendary-moth-club-now-under-threat-from-second-planning-application-for-flats-3814719?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=londons-传奇飞蛾俱乐部现在受到第二次公寓规划申请的威胁Liberty DunworthThu, 21 Nov 2024 14:07:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicIndieLive Music NewsPopPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3814719 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦 MOTH 俱乐部的现场表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该遗址于 9 月份首次受到威胁，当时向哈克尼议会提交了新开发提案</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-legendary-moth-club-now-under-threat-from-second-planning-application-for-flats-3814719">伦敦邮报传奇的 MOTH 俱乐部现在正面临第二次公寓规划申请的威胁，该俱乐部</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伦敦 MOTH 俱乐部的现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Moth-club-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦传奇的 MOTH 俱乐部再次受到威胁，第二波公寓规划申请被共享。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manchester-night-day-cardiff-fuel-post-lockdown-noise-complaints-venues-3103934">封锁后的噪音投诉威胁着曼彻斯特的夜场和日间场馆 - 但他们并不孤单</a></strong></li></ul><p>该场地位于哈克尼，自 70 年代初就存在，举办过无数现场演出、喜剧表演、电影活动和俱乐部之夜。然而，近几个月来，业主们公开表示，由于新开发计划“构成严重威胁”，该地块的未来已陷入危险。</p><p>早在九月，业主们就在社交媒体上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-moth-club-call-for-support-to-oppose-building-of-flats-that-could-pose-a-serious-threat-to-the-future-of-our-venue-3795238">呼吁当地居民和粉丝联系该行政区的规划部门</a>，对新建公寓楼的提案提出异议。</p><p>现在他们又发表了一份声明，解释了另外两项单独的提案如何提交给哈克尼议会，这可能会让他们面临风险。根据最新消息，此举旨在在晨巷开发一栋公寓楼，其中一个计划中的公寓楼设有“直接俯瞰 MOTH 吸烟区并背靠舞台墙的阳台”。</p><p>他们写道：“这两项开发项目如果获得批准，将使伦敦最受欢迎的独立草根场馆之一面临严重风险，并影响当地的形象。”他们接着解释了与场馆的距离如此之近将如何“导致冲突、噪音投诉以及对场馆运营能力的严重威胁。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCoeXWKN-1a/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div>